Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【对白】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种气势我以前曾经感到过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这气氛… 这压迫感…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我有感受过同样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以前的进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟sai重叠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天为了让小光看到我的这局棋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而延续了我千年的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\pos(400,386)}让我跟sai对弈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这风真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为 以前你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有当局者才能够看到棋盘上的奥妙之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 我也看到了那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所想的我全部都看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢老师所想的我也看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是站在今天对局的最核心的地方似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 塔矢老师一定觉得很难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然输给了sai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我输了的话 就从此引退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 一大清早就先赶来这里了 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…真的是来真的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 无论如何也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间一个拥有五项头衔的人一下子消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 在想别的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 被弄得头昏脑胀的总是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 佐为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小亮吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 不好意思 是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年成为职业棋士的进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还跟我对局过一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 我在《围棋周刊》上见过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实跟小亮同年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子 不好意思可以先离开一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然昨天老师认输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不会真的引退吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果输给sai就引退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是老师随口说的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想确认一下您的想法… 所以来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai…是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会是我!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对局中 我想起了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了以前在幽玄之间跟我下棋的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题我不会追究的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai是谁都没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和sai再对局一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在网上也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿说出名字也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老师继续上网对局的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢老师不会跟任何人说我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以偶而让sai下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 sai也会高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕…对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经感到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我体内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之轮已不由分说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不留情地转动了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经停止的时间沙漏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始滑落了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再下一局的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引退的事就当没说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦说出口就要遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次十段战第五局结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就打算履行诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便说出这样的话嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引退对我来说并不是那么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而还有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处于棋士的地位会受到很多束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不少责任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再接受那些无聊的采访
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是说不可以下棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有这个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个身体?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是头衔战 我也会认真的下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像昨天的那局一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与不知何处的某人对局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然可以下到那个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再跟sai下一次吧 进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜不透sai是何身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 跟sai有关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤？ 还是其他来探望的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 是听说名人在下网络围棋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在中间穿针引线的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢老师一定知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了嘛 不要随便说出…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是 进藤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢？ 听不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师那样是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要 这样我很难办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想跟sai下棋吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请老师收回刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然跟sai有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没没 没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,438)}绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎 你刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你设计的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai跟老师的对局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识sai对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我跟他对局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪…绪方老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识sai吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识的话 也让我跟他下棋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不知道 不认识！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然看到sai跟塔矢老师的网上对局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方先生 发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤到老师的病房里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进去时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子正在吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一些他们间的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十之八九 进藤与sai是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子是不是认识sai
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问问老师就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤和sai
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤和sai…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你跟sai对局的人是进藤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:14:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天早上在网上遇到sai要求与我对局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 你们都看到昨天的对局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为塔矢行洋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么丢脸的棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被sai走在了前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮 你也来问问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也想知道sai的真实身份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然爸爸说不知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再问也是徒劳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方先生认为sai与进藤不是同一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又拿不出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一件事是可以肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤掌握了所有谜团的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤和老师都不愿意说明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还有绪方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤回去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才进藤来过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好险 好险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来被绪方老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一点关于sai的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连塔矢也跑了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还在认为我可能就是sai吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 塔矢老师答应过我什么也不说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.02,gogo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fr6\fs25\pos(417,411)\c&H4A4AA6&}易拉罐垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过关于名人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想还有机会再让你跟他下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么愁眉苦脸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不久后就可以让你对局了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢老师会为我保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔下下也不要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的不久…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现在的我 是多么遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 昨天才刚让你下过棋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 马上就得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是引退的话 会引起很大的轰动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以暂时恐怕是不行啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用着急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的是时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间…没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光是有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谷 是这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行洋在网上下的一局吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我一直看着这个对局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常精彩的一局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 黑方是塔矢老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 那家伙也会用电脑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙应该和我一样 不认同那种东西的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 进藤 是sai啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai在网上复活了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在摆跟塔矢名人下的一局呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谷也看了那局啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 你也看了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做sai吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个持白子的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 以前我跟老师说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上有个很厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那家伙啦 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 那个sai
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白子下在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得好啊 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 这样发展下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 黑子认输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认输？在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半目胜负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白方占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子没有什么对策了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要下在这里如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是先手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看形势已经不能削弱对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 那里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这边防守一着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下在角上的话 得益将更大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 这样的话 黑子稍微占优势了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从外部被紧气的话 这一着的确很必要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下到了这地步 再回手也于事无补了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有看对的时候啊 进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谷 不要开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看到的这一着决定着胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤 学会计算了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 你平时都不计算 所以才注意到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于小光所拥有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连周围的人也开始察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小光周围闪耀着的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所没有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【GoGo】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.21,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GoGo围棋教室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:16.77,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\3c&HD554E9&\bord2\fad(50,300)\pos(433,313)}真唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:16.77,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1C79E0&\bord2\fs20\fad(50,300)\pos(175,315)}由香里老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.15,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真唯 你记得贴目吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.04,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:21.11,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近贴目由五目半变成六目半了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:21.11,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord2\fad(50,456)\pos(311,385)\3c&H137F14&}「贴目」这个给予黑子的不利条件由五目半变成了六目半！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:22.62,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:28.02,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据以往公开赛的结果 黑方的胜率明显要高
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:27.82,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord2\fad(150,300)\pos(311,388)\3c&H137F14&}过去五年间黑方胜率是51.86%！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:34.91,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord2\fad(150,300)\pos(311,388)\3c&H137F14&}中国是7目半 韩国也是6目半！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:35.07,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上中国的贴目是7目半 韩国的是6目半
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:38.41,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受此影响所以日本这次也将贴目变成了6目半
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:41.53,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是为了和 「什锦饭」区分开来才改的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:41.75,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord2\fad(150,300)\pos(311,388)\3c&H137F14&}我以为是为了和{\3c&H0000FF&}「什锦饭」{\3c&H137F14&}区分开来才改的呢~！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:41.54,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注:五目半和什锦饭在日语中发音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:44.38,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~有一点不同啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:48.89,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord2\fad(150,300)\pos(311,388)\3c&H137F14&}现在海外棋战也多了 棋士的思维也转变了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:48.89,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秀策的时代是没有 「贴目」这个概念的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:51.82,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6目半是个很大的差距呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:54.53,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\bord2\fad(150,300)\3c&H137F14&\pos(325,384)}  这次为了迎合时代变化而做的改动是半个世纪以来最大的一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.74,0:22:56.32,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围棋的规则也在跟着时代进行变化呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.35,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(495,390)}{\3c&H0000FF&}{\bord2}{\fad(250,0)\fs25}待续…
